net.myorb.math.matrices.optimization

Class MinorMatrixWrapper<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.myorb.math.matrices.AbstractMatrixWrapper<T>
      • net.myorb.math.matrices.optimization.AbstractOptimizedWrapper<T>
        • net.myorb.math.matrices.optimization.MinorMatrixWrapper<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type on which operations are to be executed
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    MatrixAccess<T>, MinorAccess<T>, OptimizedMinorAccess<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MinorMatrixComputationPool

    public class MinorMatrixWrapper<T>
extends AbstractOptimizedWrapper<T>
implements OptimizedMinorAccess<T>
    a wrapper for matrix class objects allowing minor matrix access modeled on top of full matrix. this allows reduced object creation and no copying of content into minor matrix objects
    Author:
    Michael Druckman
